          <p>Now brands are using more lively and bold colors in their ads and posts. Secondly, memes marketing has become viral. Have you ever thought about what design innovations we are going to see which will dominate the landscape in 2022? Let us highlight and summarize the top 8 graphic trends below which will prevail in 2022.</p>
