          <h5 class="mt-2">7. Quotes</h5>
          <p>Graphic design trends are cyclical. Some years back, quotes were highly in and popular. We used to see Inspirational quotes from marketing gurus, business tycoons and experts everywhere but later on people started getting bored and frustrated with the same quotes showing up all the time. Now the trend has changed slowly.</p>
          <p>LinkedIn has shared highlighting a user’s reading initiative. This quote served as social proof but it also showed that LinkedIn is engaging with its community.</p>
          <img src="media/pages/blog/Quotes.png" class="img-fluid m-2" alt="Quotes">
